ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:07:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每日去BBC 浪讀新聞15分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打<br />\n但問多句 讀新聞對日常傾計個d會唔會都有幫助</blockquote><br />\n有,但唔多<br />\n最好睇番D處境劇會好D<br />\n對話比較似日常傾計</blockquote><br />\n姐係主要都係睇同聽 跟住學佢點講野？<br />\nBtw會唔會有課程比人練英文口語 又會唔會有人去學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n方法類近係咁樣,但要練得熟<br />\n<br />\n應該會有課程教呢類.好既唔多,樓主要自己搵下邊間適合你<br />\n當然有人學,練講好多地方都有<br />\n最緊要係你聽無問題先啦.<br />\n<br />\n多問一下樓主英文咩程度?<br />\n<br />\n利申:我英文都屎</blockquote><br />\n我自己覺得聽同睇都唔錯<br />\n但講就真係好差 又要諗句式又要諗vocab <br />\nBtw Dse 英文小組討論有5<br />\n可能因為有得寫notes 所以講得順好多<br />\n但平時唔知點解好多鬼佬問我路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我答得又慢 個鬼佬又要好比心機先聽得明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab9e50823c0fb9c91a4623279cd6afda70a4708d","tid":130110,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵機會同鬼佬做朋友好過</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n唔係咁易嫁葉師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有機會我都好想識下"},{"pid":"b2bfd8f45456d914c3d4577163022aa89a79e28a","tid":130110,"uid":1095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:09:43.000Z","msg":"每星期都有同鬼佬用Skype 練説話"},{"pid":"ecc984b2289e5f97f4e6cb4224b8f3a10a83bca5","tid":130110,"uid":64628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T08:13:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每星期都有同鬼佬用Skype 練説話</blockquote><br />\n香港好多人講英文都好流利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除左留學 個個都係好似巴打你咁練返黎？"},{"pid":"5888c3223dc69a38dfbc8c89ed729f4c226d99d0","tid":130110,"uid":8345,"like":0